{"tid":336682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來一個麵包對於一啲人黎講真係好重要","createTime":"2017-07-26T15:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T16:14:08.000Z","uid":103417,"like":1757,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d30bda167ac9682432ec2c8e0d097107fab1a6","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:33:31.000Z","msg":"我從來都唔鍾意浪費食物<br />\n<br />\n叫左啲咩點都會盡量食曬佢<br />\n<br />\n但眼見依加好多香港人都真係好浪費<br />\n<br />\n叫到成枱野食左兩啖就算<br />\n<br />\n然後就話飽 格硬食咁辛苦為乜<br />\n<br />\n食唔到咁多唔該你地就叫少啲 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近做緊義工會去收一啲餐廳賣淨既麵包<br />\n<br />\n然後派比人<br />\n<br />\n我本身一直都純粹係諗住目的係唔好浪費咁派左佢<br />\n<br />\n直至今日<br />\n<br />\n我同一班清潔姐姐有溝通<br />\n<br />\n發現原來佢地真係會好感激我咁比包佢地<br />\n<br />\n一個麵包幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n對於我地黎講可能係好平<br />\n<br />\n但對於佢地黎講都會係一個負擔<br />\n<br />\n有時肚餓都唔捨得攞幾蚊去買個包<br />\n<br />\n其實聽到佢地咁講我真係好心酸<br />\n<br />\n我做到既就只可以繼續定時咁攞包比佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咁多<br />\n<br />\n其實我既目的係希望大家真係要珍惜食物<br />\n<br />\n唔係淨係第三世界先有人好慘無飽飯食<br />\n<br />\n就算香港咁近都會有呢啲事情出現<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再咁浪費啦<br />\n<br />\n嗌野食之前 諗清楚自己係咪真係有需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感激你地睇到呢到<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"43eb5b64c9a31bc0dd29085881860838afdeaa39","tid":336682,"uid":37131,"like":139,"dislike":3,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"希望香港多啲好似樓主咁既好心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3d9f25d9d41bae2c947e243b52652ccab6f203","tid":336682,"uid":19829,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T18:36:48.000Z","msg":"其實要點做先幫到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有陣時都好想盡下綿力幫到呢d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42154ead778ed7e4e50cdbe2fb0c0255a04e320b","tid":336682,"uid":74214,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:01:07.000Z","msg":"食得晒先好嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253d637f5076be0b9db194b54690311f63a8c31a","tid":336682,"uid":84646,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:08:20.000Z","msg":"樓主想問問咩義工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有時間都想做義工"},{"pid":"f0ef8f17515a10ec49649fab782698e89cf9c24f","tid":336682,"uid":37318,"like":97,"dislike":5,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實要點做先幫到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有陣時都好想盡下綿力幫到呢d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀多啲書 將來做個有權力嘅人<br />\n當你有say嘅時候 就可以影響好多人<br />\n<br />\n但其實只要本住 勿以善小而不為 勿以惡小而為之 嚟做人<br />\n世界應該可以更美好"},{"pid":"dcabead78f6e1d82e40666f6a28734f832a78d0b","tid":336682,"uid":38623,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:16:48.000Z","msg":"點樣駁: 我食唔食 佢都唔會變到有錢食到嫁/佢都唔會有野食？<br />\n利申: 由細到大 一粒米都無淨 但唔識說服人"},{"pid":"52904d9818e28fd08b3f45403588eca79a97e9c4","tid":336682,"uid":126139,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:21:04.000Z","msg":"其實而加啲麵包都唔平"},{"pid":"35874c45c54b5a2eac90ee35e9247a8af3a40cb8","tid":336682,"uid":26084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:24:08.000Z","msg":"咦我fb 都見有個人最近成日去幫手"},{"pid":"01b66e511056ff7c9d9c64de9a7251f42f19bbe8","tid":336682,"uid":54223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實而加啲麵包都唔平</blockquote><br />\n無料包都成5-8 蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf0d6b388a5587596088b2728894e9c5c14aa77","tid":336682,"uid":12741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T19:50:46.000Z","msg":"唉 聽到呢d都心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e92f0ba065f514c14ff336beac86354718d524f","tid":336682,"uid":15174,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T20:08:03.000Z","msg":