7b9021040","tid":336682,"uid":32221,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8876796a18745bc28efded17a6ec2e162d51cd1","tid":336682,"uid":59835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇自助餐<br />\n我覺得自助餐嘅意義係可以一次食到好多唔同種類嘅食物<br />\n但係見到啲人為咗回本而食<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff52b4ba5be1a816c7d3432541c473fee74d47d9","tid":336682,"uid":82103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:21:12.000Z","msg":"我都想參加，有無詳情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34b134c99df48d5b13aceecf9088b0d096e0ad3","tid":336682,"uid":83378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"想做義工 留名"},{"pid":"2a2748f8a5f743dbb54de5b2863e43d7641fc4f9","tid":336682,"uid":32221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇自助餐<br />\n我覺得自助餐嘅意義係可以一次食到好多唔同種類嘅食物<br />\n但係見到啲人為咗回本而食<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自助餐未就係試食唔同既野<br />\n好食再食多啲<br />\n回唔回本唔重要<br />\n最重要係好食<br />\n食多左會浪費？係浪費架啦<br />\n但最少有目的=為左滿足自己舌頭<br />\n不過本身我都唔特別好呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n相反為左所謂有衣食<br />\n就勉強食左幾粒飯<br />\n目的係為左乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得最on9始終都係<br />\n食左落肚就唔係浪費呢個思想"},{"pid":"6dceefd37b478682e8c944f764e7d617ba98a731","tid":336682,"uid":42425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點樣駁: 我食唔食 佢都唔會變到有錢食到嫁/佢都唔會有野食？<br />\n利申: 由細到大 一粒米都無淨 但唔識說服人</blockquote><br />\n問吓佢<br />\n去到公廁見到啲水喉開曬會唔會閂左佢？<br />\n見到個細路玩水喉會唔會行埋佢制止佢？<br />\n水費唔洗你比，你又唔會冇水洗手<br />\n閂水喉非洲細路又唔會多左水用<br />\n但你<span style=\"color: red;\">本能都一定會閂水喉</span><br />\n好簡單，因為你覺得浪費食水<br />\n咁點解食物就反而可以隨便浪費？<br />\n禁撚簡單既公民意識都要問點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlogic fail<br />\n根本唔同case</blockquote><br />\n水喉水個case比較類似buffet, 容易控制quantity<br />\n相反叫食物好容易唔小心叫多左</blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔小心叫多左唔係樓主case<br />\n因為佢唔係有心浪費，佢都係覺得自己食得曬<br />\n而最後真係眼寬肚窄左，咪知原來呢個份量自己食唔曬<br />\n下次拎少啲，唔係存心浪費<br />\n另外乜講logic 一定要同case架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f4a234903f5582a3dfeb32bca558afa5e4f4b1","tid":336682,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:41:10.000Z","msg":"諗返起琴日個二手飯post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都試過食m記叫太多野食唔曬<br />\n食緊個時有個阿叔係旁邊行黎行去<br />\n個時仲未知咩事<br />\n<br />\n跟住我食唔曬 去左廁所準備走<br />\n佢就食緊我d薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4869ccd7b68f2edc4be7ae1818843b3723d28052","tid":336682,"uid":89709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:41:22.000Z","msg":"想join呢類義工既巴絲<br />\nGoogle樂餉社bread run<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc91ea161891c2a4875fbae1d032bf932723371","tid":336682,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:59:54.000Z","msg":"從來唔鍾意食剩野<br />\n但我發現老一輩特別鐘意叫到根本你食唔晒咁多野先收手"},{"pid":"b2d293b656c00629a87d4afbe9c183f06eb32dcd","tid":336682,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"麵包鋪，便利店每日都丟緊食物<br />\n正確嚟講係銷毀緊"},{"pid":"4b51538faf567aff311ea5cadef318e8d5afae7b","tid":336682,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麵包鋪，便利店每日都丟緊食物<br />\n正確嚟講係銷毀緊</blockquote><br />\n佢地用水or 其他野整濕d面包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b161fd81ccee24730801bf001ee6db581f5aa7","tid":336682,"uid":78261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:13:03.000Z","msg":"之前返麵包舖 晚晚一落閘就dum曬d麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97203f9ece9527b0d7a232c88769f241e9fb8ffb","tid":336682,"uid":61755,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇自助餐<br />\n我覺得自助餐嘅意義係可以一次食到好多唔同種類嘅食物<br />\n但係見到啲人為咗回本而食<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自助餐未就係試食唔同既野<br />\n好食再食多啲<br />\n回唔回本唔重要<br />\n最重要係好食<br />\n食多左會浪費？係浪費架啦<br />\n但最少有目的=為左滿足自己舌頭<br />\n不過本身我都唔特別好呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n相反為左所謂有衣食<br />\n就勉強食左幾粒飯<br />\n目的係為左乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得最on9始終都係<br />\n食左落肚就唔係浪費呢個思想</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n把東西都吃完又怎麼樣？空着肚子的窮人會因為你勉力吃完而飽起來嗎？這樣做有什麼實質效果？除了可能因過食而過胖而要多花點時間去運動減肥之外！時間也是資源，我不是虛耗得更多嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n但把東西留在桌子上最後只會倒掉，這樣不是很浪費嗎？想到世界上還有多少嗷嗷待哺的人，這樣浪費良心上怎過得去？ <br />\n <br />\n不錯，浪費很令人反感，我非常反對，但勉強吃光就是不浪費嗎？浪費是指把有用的東西廢棄，這些吃剩的東西有用嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n有，食物的首要功能是維持生命，附屬功能是提供享受，當然有用。 <br />\n <br />\n不過，我之不再吃，是因為已經吃飽了，生命肯定可以維持，而勉強吃下去是個苦差，還說什麼享受！此時此刻這些吃剩的東西對我是完全沒有用的，廢棄沒用的東西怎麼可以說是浪費？ <br />\n <br />\n對你沒用但對空着肚子的人有用呀！ <br />\n<br />\n對，那麼這些食物要放進空着的肚子裏才不致浪費，自己勉強吃下去只會令本來有用的東西變成無用，這才是浪費！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCE 2009 民以食為天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e608e0074d65bb66c1ea93f4d989accb147965","tid":336682,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"珍惜食物加一，有時d frd食唔晒會幫佢食埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹因為覺得既然一個生命斷送喺我手上，我就應該尊重佢，唔可以由得佢白白犧牲"},{"pid":"7750bcd1a5bfb8f5b6d66daf37b3786b9ef7df06","tid":336682,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇自助餐<br />\n我覺得自助餐嘅意義係可以一次食到好多唔同種類嘅食物<br />\n但係見到啲人為咗回本而食<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自助餐未就係試食唔同既野<br />\n好食再食多啲<br />\n回唔回本唔重要<br />\n最重要係好食<br />\n食多左會浪費？係浪費架啦<br />\n但最少有目的=為左滿足自己舌頭<br />\n不過本身我都唔特別好呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n相反為左所謂有衣食<br />\n就勉強食左幾粒飯<br />\n目的係為左乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得最on9始終都係<br />\n食左落肚就唔係浪費呢個思想</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n把東西都吃完又怎麼樣？空着肚子的窮人會因為你勉力吃完而飽起來嗎？這樣做有什麼實質效果？除了可能因過食而過胖而要多花點時間去運動減肥之外！時間也是資源，我不是虛耗得更多嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n但把東西留在桌子上最後只會倒掉，這樣不是很浪費嗎？想到世界上還有多少嗷嗷待哺的人，這樣浪費良心上怎過得去？ <br />\n <br />\n不錯，浪費很令人反感，我非常反對，但勉強吃光就是不浪費嗎？浪費是指把有用的東西廢棄，這些吃剩的東西有用嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n有，食物的首要功能是維持生命，附屬功能是提供享受，當然有用。 <br />\n <br />\n不過，我之不再吃，是因為已經吃飽了，生命肯定可以維持，而勉強吃下去是個苦差，還說什麼享受！此時此刻這些吃剩的東西對我是完全沒有用的，廢棄沒用的東西怎麼可以說是浪費？ <br />\n <br />\n對你沒用但對空着肚子的人有用呀！ <br />\n<br />\n對，那麼這些食物要放進空着的肚子裏才不致浪費，自己勉強吃下去只會令本來有用的東西變成無用，這才是浪費！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCE 2009 民以食為天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來有人寫左篇文同我諗法完全一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b874c6c11088c5ef0588a8605230220ecb2e474a","tid":336682,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>麵包鋪，便利店每日都丟緊食物<br />\n正確嚟講係銷毀緊</blockquote><br />\n佢地用水or 其他野整濕d面包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係漂白水"},{"pid":"19235ec2f4b926056be2a0994b2f3a835cb6fe4c","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主想問問咩義工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有時間都想做義工</blockquote><br />\n間野叫做食德好<br />\n我係社職到揾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3d0b90486b660302c5373a16ae762cdc257642","tid":336682,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"社會就係咁悲哀 有人就工餐不繼<br />\n有人就幾百萬買隻錶買架車都唔幫佢地<br />\n幾百萬可能幾千幾萬人溫飽既滿足感都唔及一隻只係話比你時間既儀器<br />\n我真係睇唔通人性"},{"pid":"7b3d1eb10394ceac211a178ddb78c5a05cc64f46","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣駁: 我食唔食 佢都唔會變到有錢食到嫁/佢都唔會有野食？<br />\n利申: 由細到大 一粒米都無淨 但唔識說服人</blockquote><br />\n唔係佢有無得食既問題<br />\n而係你有得食唔食曬會好折墮既問題<br />\n不過有啲人真係好難改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c89ab8a988eead2abedaf24d2db98652a7a69f","tid":336682,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"巴打，想問問有無邊間麵包鋪會肯俾包。<br />\n因為以我所知好多連鎖店都唔肯，小弟都有心想搞，想請教吓巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fd77f1362653694a62a463372ae392070e43c8","tid":336682,"uid":77705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:46:45.000Z","msg":"屌，諗起個女仔fd例牌食淨野<br />\n冇衣食既人真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c06de350986c461ba876f18f5a69025b6b54a6","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以有陣時<br />\n我食哂自己叫嘅嘢食  俾人問我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :問您好肚餓咩/唔夠飽呀/洗唔洗食埋我嗰啲<br />\n我真係完全唔撚想應佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲真係on9 <br />\n興幸我身邊無啲咁癲既人"},{"pid":"e4542275e20844a68d59b7ae094d53bfbe20319b","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>珍惜食物係美德<br />\n<br />\n做義工就好虛偽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每日150個劣質人口，入黎搶低工資，推高物價，你做義工間唔中派兩個包幫到d咩<br />\n<br />\n你一日唔閂水喉，攞幾多隻杯去都接唔完d水</blockquote><br />\n幫到幾多得幾多<br />\n我唔會否認兩三個麵包可能真係好少<br />\n但最少收到既人真係會好開心<br />\n同埋如果連最簡單既都唔做<br />\n真係會有人無啦啦做到閂水喉呢個動作？"},{"pid":"b946be152354a4b8450e9562d62e6edd1b31d495","tid":336682,"uid":34965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以有陣時<br />\n我食哂自己叫嘅嘢食  俾人問我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :問您好肚餓咩/唔夠飽呀/洗唔洗食埋我嗰啲<br />\n我真係完全唔撚想應佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n：無 晒野好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afa8a9d1328a3e925be5b080b8a086e2d99a4e2","tid":336682,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就係多仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0add770b33f164f28aaa177a9eb0ee2b1bf536","tid":336682,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"之前唔會食剩飯個po正皮多過負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6ab60ce36629c0c0d27872db24055585a6f829","tid":336682,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:02:24.000Z","msg":"盡量食晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我叫左十碟 食得2、3碟 盡左力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor"},{"pid":"0d3f9e83bee61d4e5501060a445e8bcf249c26fc","tid":336682,"uid":57568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"之前返過麵包鋪嘅夜更<br />\n晚晚收鋪都要親手dum咗d麵包佢<br />\n我問過d麵包會去邊 佢地話會dum/餵魚....<br />\n我問可唔可以拎d走/搵人收包 佢地都話唔得....<br />\n做咗幾日無做 親手dum哂d食物 個心好唔舒服"},{"pid":"c21f6cf439043203e6176c27bb3a406a17c0264a","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盡量食晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我叫左十碟 食得2、3碟 盡左力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sor</blockquote>睇住自己食到幾多叫幾多係原則<br />\n食唔曬我自己會帶盒打包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢啲天氣好易變壞"},{"pid":"fa0a50613e8c2ec199c1f0dd0ef0abce4c82385a","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，諗起個女仔fd例牌食淨野<br />\n冇衣食既人真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有fd都係咁<br />\n無論碟野份量幾多都好<br />\n都一定要食淨先安樂<br />\n見到都嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6a4744810fe1967cc4d4e075689519f5e152a4","tid":336682,"uid":103417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，想問問有無邊間麵包鋪會肯俾包。<br />\n因為以我所知好多連鎖店都唔肯，小弟都有心想搞，想請教吓巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係喎<br />\n我做義工到個gp<br />\n見到好多都係連鎖店比包<br />\n可能要啲大機構同佢地總公司傾？"},{"pid":"fe7467b9c904a99dca2e2f344357a871f6d5dc11","tid":336682,"uid":52503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇自助餐<br />\n我覺得自助餐嘅意義係可以一次食到好多唔同種類嘅食物<br />\n但係見到啲人為咗回本而食<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自助餐未就係試食唔同既野<br />\n好食再食多啲<br />\n回唔回本唔重要<br />\n最重要係好食<br />\n食多左會浪費？係浪費架啦<br />\n但最少有目的=為左滿足自己舌頭<br />\n不過本身我都唔特別好呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n相反為左所謂有衣食<br />\n就勉強食左幾粒飯<br />\n目的係為左乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得最on9始終都係<br />\n食左落肚就唔係浪費呢個思想</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n把東西都吃完又怎麼樣？空着肚子的窮人會因為你勉力吃完而飽起來嗎？這樣做有什麼實質效果？除了可能因過食而過胖而要多花點時間去運動減肥之外！時間也是資源，我不是虛耗得更多嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n但把東西留在桌子上最後只會倒掉，這樣不是很浪費嗎？想到世界上還有多少嗷嗷待哺的人，這樣浪費良心上怎過得去？ <br />\n <br />\n不錯，浪費很令人反感，我非常反對，但勉強吃光就是不浪費嗎？浪費是指把有用的東西廢棄，這些吃剩的東西有用嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n有，食物的首要功能是維持生命，附屬功能是提供享受，當然有用。 <br />\n <br />\n不過，我之不再吃，是因為已經吃飽了，生命肯定可以維持，而勉強吃下去是個苦差，還說什麼享受！此時此刻這些吃剩的東西對我是完全沒有用的，廢棄沒用的東西怎麼可以說是浪費？ <br />\n <br />\n對你沒用但對空着肚子的人有用呀！ <br />\n<br />\n對，那麼這些食物要放進空着的肚子裏才不致浪費，自己勉強吃下去只會令本來有用的東西變成無用，這才是浪費！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCE 2009 民以食為天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來有人寫左篇文同我諗法完全一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n篇野講得啱<br />\n不過第一步要做既係食幾多叫幾多"},{"pid":"9939191e24f6b5d7ab7a6f77043690c1653e29bc","tid":336682,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來唔鍾意食剩野<br />\n但我發現老一輩特別鐘意叫到根本你食唔晒咁多野先收手</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<br />\n成日4個人叫十個餸，點食都食唔哂就好激氣<br />\n佢地覺得叫得少好寒酸"},{"pid":"9b613fda3351a73944f504c3dbe1a18a2714dfd0","tid":336682,"uid":126158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"講得好！"},{"pid":"a83a24b9141aed938348e765479e99f37d717b48","tid":336682,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54bd357475b59d6c6ce16b013dbbb2e0756c4ac","tid":336682,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:24:29.000Z","msg":"由細到大都會食到乾乾淨淨<br />\n但自從過餐廳之後<br />\n覺得自己好似係收緊人工去倒野食咁<br />\n有時我都唔明啲人裝飯果彈裝勁多<br />\n到頭來食唔哂又要倒<br />\n食幾多裝幾多真係咁難咩<br />\n每日見住呢啲野發生<br />\n總係覺得好折墜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明出面有好多人餓緊 煩緊三餐<br />\n但自己乜都做唔到<br />\n唯有就係做好自己"},{"pid":"4aa1efdbe9efd68c27b033fc5f9e5e54acc16ae4","tid":336682,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:25:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2ee1a203872d9a38ac167915c279faabcb2690d","tid":336682,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"幾蚊都唔捨得買<br />\n<br />\n清潔工都要對自己負下責任啦"},{"pid":"876b2b91aef0a2581cac1f320aa403d2f12c217b","tid":336682,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇自助餐<br />\n我覺得自助餐嘅意義係可以一次食到好多唔同種類嘅食物<br />\n但係見到啲人為咗回本而食<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自助餐未就係試食唔同既野<br />\n好食再食多啲<br />\n回唔回本唔重要<br />\n最重要係好食<br />\n食多左會浪費？係浪費架啦<br />\n但最少有目的=為左滿足自己舌頭<br />\n不過本身我都唔特別好呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n相反為左所謂有衣食<br />\n就勉強食左幾粒飯<br />\n目的係為左乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得最on9始終都係<br />\n食左落肚就唔係浪費呢個思想</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n把東西都吃完又怎麼樣？空着肚子的窮人會因為你勉力吃完而飽起來嗎？這樣做有什麼實質效果？除了可能因過食而過胖而要多花點時間去運動減肥之外！時間也是資源，我不是虛耗得更多嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n但把東西留在桌子上最後只會倒掉，這樣不是很浪費嗎？想到世界上還有多少嗷嗷待哺的人，這樣浪費良心上怎過得去？ <br />\n <br />\n不錯，浪費很令人反感，我非常反對，但勉強吃光就是不浪費嗎？浪費是指把有用的東西廢棄，這些吃剩的東西有用嗎？ <br />\n <br />\n有，食物的首要功能是維持生命，附屬功能是提供享受，當然有用。 <br />\n <br />\n不過，我之不再吃，是因為已經吃飽了，生命肯定可以維持，而勉強吃下去是個苦差，還說什麼享受！此時此刻這些吃剩的東西對我是完全沒有用的，廢棄沒用的東西怎麼可以說是浪費？ <br />\n <br />\n對你沒用但對空着肚子的人有用呀！ <br />\n<br />\n對，那麼這些食物要放進空着的肚子裏才不致浪費，自己勉強吃下去只會令本來有用的東西變成無用，這才是浪費！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCE 2009 民以食為天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來有人寫左篇文同我諗法完全一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n篇野講得啱<br />\n不過第一步要做既係食幾多叫幾多</blockquote><br />\n屌 依家係叫你要幾多叫幾多 你叫得多左野食係你自己問題 無人拎住支槍叫你叫多 你自己生活左幾十年唔知自己食野既份量？ 去到同月月"},{"pid":"e9d2f59770a8cc2983de14c921bb105865b77e81","tid":336682,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾蚊都唔捨得買<br />\n<br />\n清潔工都要對自己負下責任啦</blockquote><br />\n咁邊個對佢地嘅家庭負責任？<br />\n剩係諗自己會唔會自私左啲？<br />\n而且點解會變左係清潔工個嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974a18708b2da9e7a166ab77e626a0e5f4ed4be5","tid":336682,"uid":128869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己返飲食part time見到好多客都食淨野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次係一檯四十歲嘅女人，四、五個人，一人一杯酒，一碟雞翼都可以食唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碟雞翼一人一隻都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本人一直都好珍惜食物，除非真係好飽或者唔舒服食唔落先會放低唔要，但無奈香港太多人唔識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你呢啲思想先係浪費<br />\n你格硬食多左既只會變脂肪<br />\n或者完全吸收唔到沖左落大海<br />\n最理想一定係要食幾多就叫幾多<br />\n覺得夠就停，有剩既打包<br />\n冇得打包冇辦法，點都浪費左<br />\n好食/想食既就食埋佢，否則就算數<br />\n最梗要下次再叫少啲<br />\n<br />\n中國人有衣食呢個思想起現代on9到震<br />\n大部份人又唔駛擔又唔駛抬<br />\n勉強自己食多過需要既就唔係浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />